{"article_id":"9xyMnesqyqIfvyXS","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( SOUNDBITE )","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"( English )","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"NEW YORK STATE GOVERNOR ANDREW CUOMO SAYING :","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"\" I understand","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"that some people may think","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"the 21 day home quarantine is a burden .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"I would ask for their cooperation and understanding","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"and remember what we are trying to balance .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"We are trying to balance aid to West Africa and protection and the public health of New Yorkers and addressing the fear and concern of New Yorkers .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"We have spoken many times about the reality of Ebola .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"It is not an especially new disease .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"It was discovered in 1976 .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"It is not like the flu .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"It is not easily caught .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"All the evidence says","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"that it is transmitted through bodily fluids","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"once the person is infected and highly contagious .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"So , there is no cause for general alarm","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"but again we want the people of New York to know","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"we are staying one step ahead .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"We are doing everything possible .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"Some people will say","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"we are being too cautious .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"I will take that criticism","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"because that is better than the alternative .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"As Governor of New York , my number one job is to protect the people of New York","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"and this does that. \"","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"WHITE FLASH 3 .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"( SOUNDBITE )","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"( English )","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"NEW YORK STATE GOVERNOR ANDREW CUOMO SAYING :","depth":4},{"id":31,"text":"\" From an operational , efficiency point of view and from a safety point of view , the preferred option is to ask them to stay home .","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"The health care worker will come to their house twice a day ,","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"they can have their family ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"whoever is normally there ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"it is not that they are stopping their life .","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"They have their full life .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"But ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"if they become symptomatic ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"you will have limited the number of people","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"they will have been in contact with. \"","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"WHITE FLASH 4 .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"( SOUNDBITE )","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"( English )","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"NEW YORK STATE GOVERNOR ANDREW CUOMO SAYING :","depth":4},{"id":45,"text":"\" Well , the White House first of all and CDC will establish a protocol .","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"They are yet to establish their protocol for this situation","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"and we have to operate now .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Right , we live in the here and now .","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"Number two , whatever the CDC comes up with , they will be the first","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"to say ,","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"I believe ,","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"that they understand","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"states have different needs","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"and what New York needs , is different than what Nebraska may need ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"is different than what Kansas may need ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"is different than what Florida may need .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"So , CDC will come up with general operating protocols ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"but the states are free to design their own protocols .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"If there is a region in the country","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that has more differences than New York , New Jersey ,","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"I don ' t know of one .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"But , this will be consistent .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"It will probably be somewhat safer than what CDC comes up with","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"once they come up with their definitive protocol .","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"But , I will take that criticism","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"if you want to call it a criticism","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"that I want to be safer","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"than CDC says ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"fine . \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":139,"left":96,"right":138,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":96,"left":78,"right":95,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":78,"left":72,"right":77,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":72,"left":71,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":77,"left":74,"right":76,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":3,"right":73,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":76,"left":6,"right":75,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":75,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":85,"right":94,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":85,"left":9,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":79,"right":83,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":79,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":80,"right":82,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":80,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":14,"right":